{"tid":984781,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼重拍真人版《鐘樓駝俠》","createTime":"2019-01-17T05:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T01:11:18.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a1b55384064e574d226e36ad02efcbd4358f882a","tid":984781,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"迪士尼又傳出將發展另一部動畫改編真人版電影，也就是《鐘樓怪人》，目前已經找到編劇，將設定成一部音樂劇。<br />\n<br />\n《鐘樓怪人》動畫片於1996年上映，以維克多雨果的同名作品為原型改編，劇情描述外型醜陋但內心善良的加西莫多，在巴黎聖母院擔任敲鐘人所發生的故事。<br />\n<br />\n東尼獎得主、《蝴蝶君》華裔劇作家David Henry Hwang將擔任編劇，Alan Menken和Stephen Schwartz這對奧斯卡搭檔將負責音樂，曾演出《美女與野獸》的喬許蓋德（Josh Gad）傳出會擔任製作人和主演，但迪士尼內部知情人士透露演員尚未確定。<br />\n<br />\n迪士尼2019年將上映的動畫改編真人版電影包括《小飛象》、《阿拉丁》、《獅子王》，《花木蘭》已經殺青，計畫中的則有《木偶奇遇記》、《小美人魚》、《101忠狗》反派庫伊拉等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3839/d3839474.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3839%2Fd3839474.jpg&h=b6095a6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c743dfc1b7e2f3f23d25bb7a17b569ac081d2b41","tid":984781,"uid":67824,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"元素：黑人，同性戀，傷殘，人獸，變性"},{"pid":"ef651267377b25b08ec5bc77537d5c39d17d63ca","tid":984781,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"劇本荒到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18844660bddadd0e38d9b8d02c2c4a2aae164170","tid":984781,"uid":212399,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"迪士尼拍夠真人版電影未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e7414c4163b78ba860b11172cfb941fce485ed","tid":984781,"uid":30708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:31:57.000Z","msg":"想睇Peter Dinklage 做主角多d"},{"pid":"27ca48138dcc31c0a1940800ad28a328245d76b1","tid":984781,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef651267377b25b08ec5bc77537d5c39d17d63ca","tid":9847